      <item>
        <title>The Defaulter List</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;The spanish Tax Agency published for the second time a list of natural or legal persons who had a debt to the Treasury. 336 are individuals with a debt of 700 million. Legal persons are 4.510, with a debt of 15.000 million. Among them, still great presents real estate as Martinsa Fadesa and Aifos, the epicenter of Malaya plot that should 96 million euros. Sacyr adds with a debt of 116 million euros.
&lt;/p&gt;
